author: Scary Pockets
description:
Scary Goldings is BACK with our fifth studio album, "The Holy Enchilada". The second single "Fünf" is out on all streaming platforms now, and the full album is coming Aug 29 2025! 

Pre-order the vinyl record before October 8: https://found.ee/tdF9f0

Hear the album FIRST, join our Patreon: http://modal.scarypocketsfunk.com/patreon

Listen on Spotify: https://tinyurl.com/8shmxmfw
Tip Jar: http://modal.scarypocketsfunk.com/tips
Instagram: http://modal.scarypocketsfunk.com/instagram
Facebook: http://modal.scarypocketsfunk.com/facebook
Discord: http://modal.scarypocketsfunk.com/discord

All songs written by Larry Goldings, Ryan Lerman, Jack Conte, Kane Ritchotte, and Kaveh Rastegar.

Larry Goldings / Piano & Organ
Ryan Lerman / Guitar
Jack Conte / Keys
Kane Ritchotte / Drums
Kaveh Rastegar / Bass

Recording Engineer: Caleb Parker
Mixed by: Ryan Lerman
Produced by: Ryan Lerman
Mastered by: Ruairi O'Flaherty
Album Artwork Illustration: Barry Blitt
Digital Artwork Design: Sebi White
